{"article_id":"lH301vd4wD043G9H","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Are specific gun-control measures beginning to build momentum in Congress ?","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"Key lawmakers in recent comments have indicated","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that ' s the case .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"For instance , Sen. John McCain","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"( R )","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"of Arizona on Sunday said","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"many senators are lining up behind a bipartisan plan","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"whose centerpiece is an expansion of background checks on gun purchasers .","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"\" I think","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"that most of us will be able to support \" that package ,","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"said Senator McCain on NBC ' s `` Meet the Press . ''","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"Background checks have long been seen as a sweet spot in the gun debate","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"that could draw both Republican and Democratic votes ,","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"but McCain ' s tacit endorsement is still a \" key moment , \"","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"writes liberal-leaning Greg Sargent in his Plum Line Washington Post blog .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"The bipartisan group","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"that ' s pulling the plan together","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"includes Sen. Joe Manchin of West Virginia , a key pro-gun Democrat , and conservative GOP Sen. Tom Coburn of Oklahoma ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"Mr. Sargent notes .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"It would include expanded sharing of data on mental illness","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"and likely have some sort of provision","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"ensuring","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"that the checks don ' t lead to a national registry of gun owners .","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"\" Having Coburn and Manchin bless such a proposal would give it a major boost , even among GOP lawmakers","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"inclined to robotically do whatever the NRA","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"[ National Rifle Association ]","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"tells them to do , \"","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"he writes .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"This doesn ' t mean the plan is tied up with ribbon and a bow ;","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"another member of the bipartisan effort , Sen. Chuck Schumer","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"( D )","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"of New York ,","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"added on Sunday","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"that the group has made good progress","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"but still has some hard issues to resolve .","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"\" Guns [ are ] a very difficult issue , \"","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"said Senator Schumer on CNN ' s `` State of the Union . ''","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"Asked whether a ban on assault weapons would be included in the Senate ' s package ,","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"Schumer side-stepped the issue .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"He noted","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"that Sen. Dianne Feinstein","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"( D )","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"of California","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"has introduced legislation","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"to prohibit such military-style firearms","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"and said","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"that her bill will get a vote on the Senate floor .","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"\" Whether it ' s part of our bill ,","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"we ' ve been focusing on universal background checks ,","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"where I think","depth":14},{"id":50,"text":"there ' s a greater chance","depth":15},{"id":51,"text":"to come to a bipartisan agreement , \"","depth":15},{"id":52,"text":"said Schumer .","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"( Currently , federal law requires background checks only for customers of federally licensed firearm dealers .","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"They aren ' t required for private transactions ,","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"many of which occur at gun shows .","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"Some states have more stringent check requirements of their own . )","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"Another gun provision","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"the Senate might be able to pass","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"is a new federal law against firearms trafficking .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"In essence , this would give prosecutors another way","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"to go after those","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"who legally purchase guns","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"and then pass them to others","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"who use them","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"to commit crimes .","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"It ' s also possible the Senate will at least seriously consider proposals","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"to ban high-capacity ammunition magazines , as well .","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"Sen. Frank Lautenberg","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"( D )","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"of New Jersey has introduced legislation","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"that would ban any magazine","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"that holds more than 10 rounds .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"\" There is no place in our communities for military-style supersized magazines like those","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"used inside Sandy Hook Elementary School , in Aurora , and in Tucson , \"","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"said Senator Lautenberg last month","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"when he introduced the bill .","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"It ' s important to remember that the Senate is but the first hurdle for any new gun curbs .","depth":3},{"id":78,"text":"They ' d have to pass the GOP-controlled House , as well ,","depth":4},{"id":79,"text":"where it ' s less clear","depth":5},{"id":80,"text":"there ' s any consensus for new measures .","depth":5},{"id":81,"text":"Get the Monitor Stories","depth":5},{"id":82,"text":"you care about","depth":5},{"id":83,"text":"delivered to your inbox .","depth":4},{"id":84,"text":"By signing up ,","depth":4},{"id":85,"text":"you agree to our Privacy Policy","depth":4},{"id":86,"text":"Senate Judiciary Committee Chairman Patrick Leahy","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"( D )","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"of Vermont ,","depth":6},{"id":89,"text":"a key player in the issue on the Senate side , said over the weekend","depth":5},{"id":90,"text":"that it is his understanding that the House will just wait to see what the Senate does ,","depth":5},{"id":91,"text":"and then decide upon its plan of action .","depth":5},{"id":92,"text":"\" They feel","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"if we ' re able to do something","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"there might be a chance .","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"If we ' re unable ,","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"frankly , they ' re not going to try anything at all .","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"I think","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"that ' s a political reality , \"","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"Senator Leahy told NPR 's `` Weekend Edition '' on Saturday .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":199,"left":180,"right":198,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":180,"left":176,"right":179,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":176,"left":0,"right":175,"relation":"topic","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":175,"left":126,"right":174,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":101,"right":125,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":125,"left":112,"right":124,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":108,"right":111,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":108,"left":105,"right":107,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":103,"right":104,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":103,"left":102,"right":5,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":102,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":6,"right":7,"re